" Recommended key-mappings.
" <CR>: close popup and save indent.
fun! s:my_cr_func()
	return pumvisible() ? neocomplcache#smart_close_popup() : "\<CR>"
endfun
"inoremap <expr><CR>  neocomplcache#smart_close_popup()."\<CR>"
